00:15:17,987 --> 00:15:19,507
Lady, please wait for me a moment,

254
00:15:36,147 --> 00:15:39,927
Lady Liuli, look how this turned out,

255
00:15:39,927 --> 00:15:42,547
Lady Liuli,
please hurry and persuade Lady Cen for me,

256
00:15:42,547 --> 00:15:45,667
She has come to clear my grievances
and to vindicate my husband,

257
00:15:45,667 --> 00:15:46,707
Why should I persuade her then?

258
00:15:51,027 --> 00:15:53,867
Lady Liuli, as long as you are willing to stop,

259
00:15:53,867 --> 00:15:56,587
then you'll be in charge of the Luoyang estate
from now on,

260
00:15:57,267 --> 00:16:00,487
I will help you get the deed to the property,
how about that?

261
00:16:00,487 --> 00:16:02,387
Are you losing your mind?

262
00:16:03,107 --> 00:16:05,447
Today's matter concerns the reputation of
Pei family,

263
00:16:05,447 --> 00:16:08,227
What does it have to do with the property
in Luoyang?

264
00:16:08,227 --> 00:16:09,547
How can this be used as a transaction?

265
00:16:09,547 --> 00:16:11,707
- Isn't this just someone having a guilty conscience?
- Yes, it is,

266
00:16:12,267 --> 00:16:13,312
It's a disgrace to me!

267
00:16:19,267 --> 00:16:21,907
Lady, get up, Quickly help her up,

268
00:16:22,947 --> 00:16:24,667
Come on,

269
00:16:39,387 --> 00:16:42,707
Princess,
take care of your body, don't be angry,

270
00:16:48,987 --> 00:16:52,347
Where is Cui? And that hussy, Shanhu?

271
00:16:52,347 --> 00:16:53,987
Where the hell are they going?

272
00:17:00,907 --> 00:17:01,952
Madam,

273
00:17:05,787 --> 00:17:07,827
you are becoming more and more 'smart',

274
00:17:08,827 --> 00:17:10,427
What were you thinking?

275
00:17:11,187 --> 00:17:13,747
Mentioned Luoyang estate
in front of everyone to Liuli?

276
00:17:14,347 --> 00:17:16,507
Are you not making trouble out of nothing?

277
00:17:19,187 --> 00:17:20,667
I'm not efficient in handling things,

278
00:17:21,587 --> 00:17:24,627
Madam, punish me,

279
00:17:31,507 --> 00:17:32,640
Where is Shanhu?

280
00:17:33,147 --> 00:17:36,947
Madam, Shanhu is now resting in her room
after being heavily punished,

281
00:17:36,947 --> 00:17:38,147
Rest?

282
00:17:41,547 --> 00:17:46,227
Very good, messed things up,

283
00:17:46,227 --> 00:17:49,547
and she dare to lie down and rest comfortably
in the room?

284
00:18:15,387 --> 00:18:17,427
I have let you down, Madam,

285
00:18:17,427 --> 00:18:20,227
Please, give me another chance,

286
00:18:22,867 --> 00:18:23,867
Madam!

287
00:18:29,667 --> 00:18:31,547
I'll find an imperial physician
from the Imperial Hospital now,

288
00:18:36,747 --> 00:18:38,547
Give you another chance?

289
00:18:40,467 --> 00:18:42,827
I'm afraid what you're saying isn't sincere,

290
00:18:45,387 --> 00:18:46,707
I am speaking from the heart,

291
00:18:47,307 --> 00:18:49,647
Where the Princess can make use of me,

292
00:18:49,647 --> 00:18:53,667
I would willingly be crushed to dust
and broken to pieces,

293
00:18:55,427 --> 00:18:58,947
Willingly be crushed to dust
and broken to pieces?

294
00:19:02,187 --> 00:19:05,947
Alright, keep your word,

295
00:19:11,227 --> 00:19:14,627
I… I would even be crushed to dust

296
00:19:15,867 --> 00:19:17,107
and be willingly broken to pieces,

297
00:19:21,827 --> 00:19:22,827
Fine, Shanhu,

298
00:19:25,027 --> 00:19:29,107
Then, I will give you another chance,

299
00:19:30,947 --> 00:19:34,947
Take Shanhu away and punish her heavily!

300
00:19:35,787 --> 00:19:37,427
Beat her heavily!

301
00:19:37,987 --> 00:19:40,387
Do not stop without my orders,

302
00:19:42,027 --> 00:19:43,547
No, no!

303
00:19:44,787 --> 00:19:48,947
Please! Please!

304
00:19:49,587 --> 00:19:52,907
Please! My Princess!

305
00:19:54,307 --> 00:19:55,392
Cui,

306
00:19:59,587 --> 00:20:01,467
Go and receive ten planks by yourself,

307
00:20:02,507 --> 00:20:04,907
If you dare to do wrong things again,
you'll end up like Shanhu,

308
00:20:26,852 --> 00:20:30,784
<i>[House of Gold and Jade]</i>

309
00:20:34,587 --> 00:20:38,267
Lu, I have a task for you to handle,

310
00:20:41,467 --> 00:20:42,547
Please give your instructions, Madam,

311
00:20:43,267 --> 00:20:46,787
This matter, we still need to pin it on Shanhu,

312
00:20:48,147 --> 00:20:51,507
Just say it's a joke stemming from the discord
between the sisters,

313
00:20:54,827 --> 00:20:55,840
If that's the case,

314
00:20:56,947 --> 00:20:59,227
then we must cheat Shanhu,

315
00:21:00,427 --> 00:21:02,867
I wonder
why Madam wants to teach her a lesson again?

316
00:21:17,827 --> 00:21:19,027
My lord, my lady,

317
00:21:20,267 --> 00:21:22,027
There is new activity
in the Residence of the Hedong Duke again,

318
00:21:22,667 --> 00:21:24,507
The imperial physician
who was invited into the mansion a few days ago

319
00:21:24,507 --> 00:21:25,747
was came in three times a day,

320
00:21:25,747 --> 00:21:27,707
But as of yesterday,
it was changed to once a day,

321
00:21:28,267 --> 00:21:30,387
However, today they have invited another one,

322
00:21:30,387 --> 00:21:32,867
A familiar traumatologist
has entered the mansion,

323
00:21:32,867 --> 00:21:34,187
I don't know

324
00:21:35,507 --> 00:21:38,447
why they visit three times a day
instead of visiting once a day,

325
00:21:38,447 --> 00:21:40,587
which indicates
that the Princess is getting better,

326
00:21:41,427 --> 00:21:44,507
But why did they call for a trauma doctor?

327
00:21:46,427 --> 00:21:50,307
Cheng, send someone to closely watch them
in the Residence of the Hedong Duke,

328
00:21:50,827 --> 00:21:52,067
Also find someone to go to the Kudi's Mansion,

329
00:21:52,627 --> 00:21:56,147
Just say that I will visit my father-in-law
today,

330
00:21:56,827 --> 00:21:57,888
Yes, my lord,

331
00:22:06,187 --> 00:22:07,707
Cao, don't blame me for being ruthless,

332
00:22:08,507 --> 00:22:09,807
I have warned you long ago

333
00:22:09,807 --> 00:22:11,707
that Liuli has already changed a lot now,

334
00:22:11,707 --> 00:22:12,867
You must not make the mistake again,

335
00:22:13,467 --> 00:22:15,667
Shanhu has just been married to them
for a few days,

336
00:22:15,667 --> 00:22:16,947
and there has this kind of trouble,

337
00:22:18,387 --> 00:22:20,187
Even though Liuli hasn't told me personally,

338
00:22:20,187 --> 00:22:21,947
but it's already being wildly talked about
outside,

339
00:22:21,947 --> 00:22:24,347
They say that Shanhu holds a grudge
against her own sister,

340
00:22:24,347 --> 00:22:27,327
and plotted against her sister
at the Princess's Lotus Banquet

341
00:22:27,327 --> 00:22:28,907
to set a trap
to ruin her elder sister's reputation,

342
00:22:29,787 --> 00:22:31,467
Shouyue has made an appointment to come over
today,

343
00:22:31,467 --> 00:22:32,787
certainly to demand an explanation,

344
00:22:33,467 --> 00:22:34,827
If you guys don't want to make things well,
then forget it,

345
00:22:35,347 --> 00:22:37,107
Why do you have to jeopardize my future?

346
00:22:39,267 --> 00:22:41,707
My lord, Mr, Pei's carriage has arrived,

347
00:22:42,787 --> 00:22:43,872
Really?

348
00:22:45,347 --> 00:22:46,467
Quickly, lock her door,

349
00:22:52,147 --> 00:22:53,184
You go first, I'll handle this,

350
00:22:58,387 --> 00:22:59,456
Shouyue,

351
00:23:01,347 --> 00:23:02,400
Father-in-law,

352
00:23:02,944 --> 00:23:04,047
No need to be polite,

353
00:23:04,047 --> 00:23:06,627
I have some business matters to consult you on,

354
00:23:06,627 --> 00:23:07,707
Hurry, hurry, please come inside,

355
00:23:08,932 --> 00:23:09,632
<i>[Prosperity, Luck, and Wellbeing]</i>

356
00:23:11,307 --> 00:23:13,347
I have just prepared some fine tea,

357
00:23:13,347 --> 00:23:15,867
and I have never had the heart to drink it,
waiting for you to come and brew it,

358
00:23:15,867 --> 00:23:17,267
Come inside, please have a try,

359
00:23:23,587 --> 00:23:25,227
Taste it, Shouyue,

360
00:23:27,307 --> 00:23:28,320
Thank you very much,

361
00:23:30,227 --> 00:23:32,507
Why haven't I seen Lady Cao today?

362
00:23:37,507 --> 00:23:38,907
She is sick,

363
00:23:39,987 --> 00:23:41,147
She's so confused because of sickness,

364
00:23:41,987 --> 00:23:43,647
I've had a doctor look at her,

365
00:23:43,647 --> 00:23:46,307
The doctor said
she's suffering from a phlegm obstruction,

366
00:23:47,467 --> 00:23:48,467
It's not convenient for her to meet others,

367
00:23:49,547 --> 00:23:52,187
So I've arranged for her to recuperate
in the side room,

368
00:23:54,067 --> 00:23:56,787
I suspect she's suffering from some heatstroke
due to the sweltering summer,

369
00:23:57,547 --> 00:23:58,627
Yes, that's right,

370
00:23:58,627 --> 00:24:02,127
Luckily,
I've prepared some platters of melon and fruit

371
00:24:02,127 --> 00:24:03,787
to relieve the summer heat at home,

372
00:24:03,787 --> 00:24:06,887
This time I want to invite you and Lady Cao

373
00:24:06,887 --> 00:24:08,307
to spend a couple of days at my place,

374
00:24:08,867 --> 00:24:11,427
It seems that only you can go to my place now,

375
00:24:11,987 --> 00:24:13,947
I wonder if you have any other arrangements
in the next two days?

376
00:24:15,227 --> 00:24:16,387
No arrangements,

377
00:24:17,107 --> 00:24:18,112
That's great,

378
00:24:19,067 --> 00:24:21,247
The weather is very pleasant today,

379
00:24:21,247 --> 00:24:22,587
carriage is waiting at the door,

380
00:24:22,587 --> 00:24:26,144
Why don't you come with me right now?

381
00:24:26,144 --> 00:24:27,187
Now?

382
00:24:27,187 --> 00:24:28,224
Yes,

383
00:24:28,827 --> 00:24:31,927
Okay then, wait here, Shouyue,

384
00:24:31,927 --> 00:24:33,187
I'll go get ready,

385
00:24:33,187 --> 00:24:34,208
Alright,

386
00:24:48,627 --> 00:24:49,867
Let me out!

387
00:24:52,267 --> 00:24:53,707
Let me out!

388
00:24:54,867 --> 00:24:57,267
I have something to say to Mr, Pei,

389
00:24:58,547 --> 00:24:59,667
Shouyue, ignore her, just ignore her,

390
00:24:59,667 --> 00:25:03,667
Pei Xingjian, every debt has its debtor,
every wrong has its wrongdoer,

391
00:25:04,827 --> 00:25:09,792
I was the one
who wronged Liuli and her mother back then,

392
00:25:09,792 --> 00:25:10,627
<i>[Prosperity, Luck, and Wellbeing]</i>

393
00:25:10,627 --> 00:25:12,307
I deserve my punishment,

394
00:25:14,027 --> 00:25:17,947
I beg you, please save Shanhu's life,

395
00:25:18,747 --> 00:25:21,427
She is Liuli's blood sister,

396
00:25:24,027 --> 00:25:25,587
If you are so heartless,

397
00:25:26,347 --> 00:25:30,427
if you harm each other,
then you will face retribution,

398
00:25:40,227 --> 00:25:44,007
What… what are you still stunned about?
Hurry up and gag her!

399
00:25:44,007 --> 00:25:45,147
- Yes,
- Wait,

400
00:25:46,427 --> 00:25:50,307
If that's the case,
I'd like to hear Lady Cao's thought,

401
00:26:00,267 --> 00:26:01,907
Why don't you take care of your illness,
what are you messing around for?

402
00:26:03,027 --> 00:26:05,667
Mr, Pei, Sir,

403
00:26:06,587 --> 00:26:07,907
Think about it, Mr, Pei,

404
00:26:09,187 --> 00:26:10,787
Although Shanhu is immature,

405
00:26:11,627 --> 00:26:13,667
she has only been married for a few days,

406
00:26:14,667 --> 00:26:16,627
How dare she do such a thing?

407
00:26:18,067 --> 00:26:20,147
They are under someone's orders and dispatch,

408
00:26:21,147 --> 00:26:22,176
If you and Liuli

409
00:26:22,176 --> 00:26:24,567
are willing to visit Princess Linhai
and persuade her,

410
00:26:24,567 --> 00:26:26,227
you will definitely be able to save her life,

411
00:26:26,227 --> 00:26:27,296
What do you mean by this?

412
00:26:28,147 --> 00:26:30,027
Shanhu is the daughter-in-law of them,

413
00:26:31,027 --> 00:26:33,067
since she is following the orders
of the Princess,

414
00:26:33,827 --> 00:26:35,147
then how can there be any concerns
about her life?

415
00:26:37,667 --> 00:26:41,067
I heard that something happened
at the Lotus Banquet that day,

416
00:26:42,667 --> 00:26:45,027
then I secretly visited there,
the Residence of the Hedong Duke for twice,

417
00:26:46,347 --> 00:26:47,747
But I didn't see anyone at all,

418
00:26:49,067 --> 00:26:51,247
Later on, I cost some money,

419
00:26:51,247 --> 00:26:53,707
only then did a servant secretly tell me,

420
00:26:55,147 --> 00:26:57,267
Princess Linhai became furious,

421
00:26:57,987 --> 00:26:59,907
She wished she could take Shanhu's life,

422
00:27:01,507 --> 00:27:02,592
This…

423
00:27:03,467 --> 00:27:08,267
If you… if you are willing to persuade them,

424
00:27:09,307 --> 00:27:11,067
I will be indebted to you in my next life,
whatever it cost,

425
00:27:11,867 --> 00:27:14,227
Never will I forget your great kindness,

426
00:27:15,827 --> 00:27:19,847
Neither I nor my daughter
dare to offend Liuli anymore,

427
00:27:19,847 --> 00:27:23,927
If we dare to offend Liuli again,
we'll go to hell and never be reincarnated,

428
00:27:23,927 --> 00:27:25,187
There's no need to swear oaths anymore,

429
00:27:27,147 --> 00:27:30,147
Mostly thanks to you
that Shanhu has what she has today,

430
00:27:31,707 --> 00:27:34,227
If I remember correctly,
you made a venomous oath last time,

431
00:27:34,867 --> 00:27:37,987
saying that if auntie crosses Liuli again
in any way,

432
00:27:38,547 --> 00:27:40,387
you and your daughter
will never have a good day,

433
00:27:42,187 --> 00:27:43,427
It seems that heaven has eyes,

434
00:27:44,427 --> 00:27:46,227
Oaths are not made lightly,

435
00:27:47,187 --> 00:27:49,707
Your aunt simply fulfilled the vow you made,

436
00:27:51,307 --> 00:27:52,667
This is karmic retribution,

437
00:27:59,427 --> 00:28:00,448
Father-in-law,

438
00:28:01,787 --> 00:28:02,880
Please,

439
00:28:09,707 --> 00:28:13,187
Mr, Pei, Mr, Pei!

440
00:28:19,172 --> 00:28:24,067
<i>[Ruyi Fabric Printing Shop]</i>

441
00:28:24,067 --> 00:28:25,120
Yah!

442
00:28:27,827 --> 00:28:29,547
Yah! Whoa!

443
00:28:33,387 --> 00:28:34,827
Father-in-law, please wait a moment

444
00:28:36,676 --> 00:28:39,392
<i>[Ruyi Fabric Printing Shop]</i>

445
00:28:39,392 --> 00:28:40,416
Liuli,

446
00:28:40,416 --> 00:28:42,467
You didn't allow me to visit father's house
today,

447
00:28:42,467 --> 00:28:43,987
and you didn't allow me to stay at home either,

448
00:28:43,987 --> 00:28:46,567
Instead, you let me wait here for you,
What's going on?

449
00:28:46,567 --> 00:28:47,947
We have guests at home today,

450
00:28:47,947 --> 00:28:50,707
It's not good for you to go home alone,
Just follow me home and you'll know,

451
00:28:56,307 --> 00:28:57,344
Whoa!

452
00:29:02,148 --> 00:29:06,464
<i>[Pei's Mansion]</i>

453
00:29:20,387 --> 00:29:22,107
My Lord, My Lady, Mr, Kudi,

454
00:29:22,787 --> 00:29:24,987
Lady Lu of the Residence of the Hedong Duke
has come visiting unexpectedly,

455
00:29:24,987 --> 00:29:27,587
They carried a sickly lady off the carriage,

456
00:29:27,587 --> 00:29:29,847
She says the sick lady has come to apologize,

457
00:29:29,847 --> 00:29:32,067
I told her you both were out,
but she insisted on waiting,

458
00:29:32,667 --> 00:29:35,267
It was too undignified for them to stay
outside the door,

459
00:29:35,267 --> 00:29:36,587
so I sent them in,

460
00:29:36,587 --> 00:29:37,667
Now, the whole party

461
00:29:37,667 --> 00:29:39,107
are waiting in the front courtyard's hall,

462
00:29:40,027 --> 00:29:42,507
Could that woman b-b-be Shanhu?

463
00:29:43,147 --> 00:29:46,807
Cheng, go to the Autumn Courtyard
and invite Physician Xiao to the hall,

464
00:29:46,807 --> 00:29:48,267
Yes, my lord,

465
00:29:48,267 --> 00:29:50,087
Father-in-law, Madam Lu

466
00:29:50,087 --> 00:29:52,027
is the second daughter-in-law
of Princess Linhai,

467
00:29:52,027 --> 00:29:54,207
She has come to visit suddenly,
and has brought someone with her,

468
00:29:54,207 --> 00:29:57,547
Presumably,
the Princess has punished Shanhu heavily,

469
00:29:57,547 --> 00:30:01,547
Is that so? W-W-What should we do?

470
00:30:02,547 --> 00:30:05,307
I wanted to invite you to spend a few days
leisurely,

471
00:30:05,307 --> 00:30:06,947
but I didn't expect to encounter such a thing,

472
00:30:08,187 --> 00:30:10,627
The plan now is to go and take a look first,

473
00:30:12,644 --> 00:30:16,256
<i>[Pei's Mansion]</i>

474
00:30:22,244 --> 00:30:23,520
<i>[Benevolence Through Actions]</i>

475
00:30:30,107 --> 00:30:31,667
Brother, Sister-in-law,

476
00:30:34,387 --> 00:30:37,547
I come uninvited today, please forgive me,

477
00:30:38,387 --> 00:30:40,707
No need for formalities, This is my father,

478
00:30:45,347 --> 00:30:48,147
Please tell me, Lady Lu,
what happened to Shanhu?

479
00:30:49,427 --> 00:30:51,167
I want you to know

480
00:30:51,167 --> 00:30:53,547
that the matter of the Lotus Banquet that day
has been clarified,

481
00:30:54,787 --> 00:30:56,667
It was all planned by your sister alone,

482
00:30:57,627 --> 00:31:00,347
The Princess gave me the divorce letter
written by the Crown Prince

483
00:31:00,347 --> 00:31:01,408
and hand it to you,

484
00:31:01,947 --> 00:31:05,227
After this, Shanhu has nothing to do with us,

485
00:31:05,747 --> 00:31:07,667
You can deal with her at will,

486
00:31:07,667 --> 00:31:10,307
don't care about the face of us,

487
00:31:12,147 --> 00:31:15,627
B-B-But Shanhu has just been married
for a few days,

488
00:31:16,267 --> 00:31:17,987
how could you decide to divorce just like that?

489
00:31:19,987 --> 00:31:21,227
Shanhu's marriage arrangements

490
00:31:21,947 --> 00:31:24,267
was agreed by the Residence of the Hedong Duke
and my father,

491
00:31:24,267 --> 00:31:25,667
Liuli was not informed,

492
00:31:26,387 --> 00:31:29,627
No matter what the issue is today,
it should still be decided by my father,

493
00:31:31,187 --> 00:31:33,707
Father, what do you think?

494
00:31:38,987 --> 00:31:40,827
It's all because of my confusion,

495
00:31:42,307 --> 00:31:44,547
This has not only caused complete unrest,

496
00:31:46,147 --> 00:31:48,547
but… but also delayed Shanhu's future,

497
00:31:50,387 --> 00:31:52,707
The Residence of the Hedong Duke destroy people
utterly,

498
00:31:53,507 --> 00:31:54,827
it's okay if we don't go back,

499
00:32:03,387 --> 00:32:04,448
Shanhu,

500
00:32:06,147 --> 00:32:07,427
I will take you home,

501
00:32:13,627 --> 00:32:14,688
Please,

502
00:32:31,067 --> 00:32:33,007
Mr, Pei, may I be bold to ask,

503
00:32:33,007 --> 00:32:35,587
