until this time?

504
00:32:36,467 --> 00:32:38,767
It seems okay now,

505
00:32:38,767 --> 00:32:41,587
but it's the affection of ginseng soup,

506
00:32:42,627 --> 00:32:46,467
I… I'm afraid it won't last more than two days,

507
00:33:04,307 --> 00:33:06,147
Don't let Shanhu live,

508
00:33:07,827 --> 00:33:11,707
Beat her half to death and then keep her alive
with ginseng soup,

509
00:33:12,267 --> 00:33:16,187
Send her into Pei Shouyue's mansion,
and let Liuli deal with her,

510
00:33:17,067 --> 00:33:19,547
As long as Shanhu dies in Liuli's mansion,

511
