513
00:33:27,827 --> 00:33:31,747
Then Liuli developed a grudge and killed her
in return,

514
00:33:34,707 --> 00:33:36,747
Liuli's concubine mother is a shrew,

515
00:33:37,547 --> 00:33:39,387
