543
00:35:54,867 --> 00:35:55,872
Please,

544
00:36:00,307 --> 00:36:03,387
Shanhu is blessed with good fortune,
and Mr, Xiao has superb medical skills,

545
00:36:03,947 --> 00:36:05,067
